<h1>How to install OpenGL</h1>

<p>sudo apt-get install freeglut3 -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install binutils-gold -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install g++ cmake -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install libglew-dev -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install g++ -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install mesa-common-dev -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install mesa-common-dev -y <\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install libglew1.5-dev libglm-dev -y<\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install libsoil-dev<\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install libglew-dev<\p>
<p>sudo apt-get install libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev <\p>

<h1>How to compile</h1>
<p>make<\p>
<p>make clean<\p>
<p>./tp1<\p>